sources.title: Sixteen Fathoms Deep (1934) LON CHANEY JR
sources.description:
Stars: Lon Chaney Jr., Sally O'Neil, Russell Simpson 
Director: Armand Schaefer

A sponge diver hopes to make enough money to buy his own boat and marry his girlfriend. A rival diver, however, has other plans for him
